    Constructs the permutation embedding from a given time-series.
    
    Arguments:
        ts:
            A one-dimensional Numpy array with dtype = "double." The time-series. 
        dim:
            The integer embedding dimension.
        lag:
            The integer embedding lag.
    
    Returns:
